<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śākavaruṣaṁbhulu 1309 gunēṭi mākha kṛṣṇa
<lb n="2" break="no"/>Ēkādaśiyu ravivāramunāṁḍu vārāṇasikaṭakāna 
<lb n="3"/>rabyedēvujīyanaṁgāri koḍuku gōviṁdamahāpātruṁḍu
<lb n="4"/>tanaku Abhīṣṭārtthaśiddhigānu śrīnarasiṁhyānathuniki
<lb n="5"/>nityamunnu Ubhayadhūpālānnu parimāṟanu reṁḍu ve
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṁjyamaramulu samarppiṁcenu I sāmaralu parimā
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ṟānu sānulaṁdu nāgadēva narasihyarēḍḍi kuṁtuṟu Ōba
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ḷasāni mruggu tiruvaḍireḍḍi kuṁtuṟu Akkasāni saṁpra
<lb n="9" break="no"/>dāyamaṁdu varadanabhōḍiga varadasāni kuṁtuṟu gaṁgga
<lb n="10" break="no"/>sāni [Āmajugāpūpērasā]ni kuṁtuṟu tallasāni vīri
<lb n="11"/>I nalugurakunnu prasādamu kuṁcalu 4 śrībhaṁḍḍara(ṁ)ma
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ṁdu padmanidhi veṁḍiṭaṁkalu Iruvainalugu 24 peṭi I prasā
<lb n="13" break="no"/>damu vṛttigā koni I nalu<supplied reason="omitted">gu</supplied>rakunu peṭenu vīru I pra
<lb n="14" break="no"/>sādamu bhujiṁci I kolupulu Ācaṁdra<unclear>rkka</unclear>staIgānu
<lb n="15"/>koluvāṁgalāru nibaṁdasamasya <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ī dha<unclear>mmu</unclear> śrīvaiṣṇava ra<unclear>kṣa</unclear>
</p>

